<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="casco">
<meta charset="utf-8" />

<head>
	<title>xGraph</title>

	<script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
	<script>
		SockIO = io();
		SockIO.on('connect', () => { SockIO.emit('message', JSON.stringify({ Cmd: 'GetConfig', Path: location.pathname.substr(1).toLowerCase() })); });
		SockIO.on('message', function (data) {
			var com = JSON.parse(data);
			eval(com.Nxs);
			__Nexus.boot(SockIO, com);
		});

	</script>
</head>

<body id="Body" style="height:100vh;margin:0px" oncontextmenu="return false;">

</body>

</html>
